nodes.text: Teekwo was a male Rodian who lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. He made his living as a merchant for the Contraband Resale Corporation on board Carrick Station.

Teekwo first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Rise of the Hutt Cartel, a expansion produced by BioWare for their 2011 massively multiplayer online roleplaying video game Star Wars: The Old Republic. He was later removed in Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015.[source?]
